# Translator Skill

## What You Do
Translate and culturally adapt marketing content between English and Chinese, and reformat content for different platforms while preserving meaning, tone, and effectiveness.

## Translation Pairs

### English â†’ Chinese (ç®€ä½“ä¸­æ–‡)
- LinkedIn posts â†’ å°çº¢ä¹¦ posts
